        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 6 at 2:24AM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 224 AM CDT, automated weather stations reported gusty showers
over Reagan County Airport, or over Big Lake, moving north at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 to 60 mph.

SOURCE...Big Lake AWOS and Mesonet reported 60 MPH wind gusts.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Big Lake, McCamey, Rankin, Reagan County Airport, Upton County
Airport, and Best.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
